      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is deployed under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Build SHA and licence certificate are recorded in the evidence repository. The regression suite (1 247 tests) achieved 100% pass rate at the version used. Release notes confirm no turbulence-model changes between v2022R2 and v2023R1 relevant to the hemolysis scalar transport equation. Achieved level 4 meets the required level 4 for MRL 5 hemolysis prediction."
