      "rationale": "Validation comparison performed per ASME V&V 20-2009. Validation uncertainty U_val = sqrt(U_num² + U_exp²) computed at each operating point. All five CFD NIH predictions lie within ±U_val(k=2) of experimental means. Feature-based validation index (FBVI) ≥ 0.91 across all planes. The depth of the quantitative comparison, including full uncertainty decomposition, supports achieved level 5, exceeding the required level 4."
