      "rationale": "Validation experiments were performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry (STL file hash SHA-256: a3f9…c12e), identical to the COU simulation geometry. All five COU operating points are represented in the validation matrix. CFD boundary conditions (inlet mass flow rate, outlet static pressure) were set to match experimental measurements within ±0.3%. Achieved level 4 meets the MRL 5 requirement."
