      },
      "rationale": "Fluid properties in validation simulations were set to match experimental blood analogue measurements (μ = 0.00356 Pa·s, ρ = 1050 kg/m³) within 0.5%. Pump geometry is identical (same STL file, hash-verified). Rotational speeds and flow rates in validation simulations match experimental set-points within ±0.2% (within instrument calibration uncertainty). A formal equivalency table (Table 4 of the evidence report) documents all 17 input parameters with COU vs. validation values and assessed impact. Achieved level 4 meets requirement."
